{"tid":1562242,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你公司仆街嘅話做細嘅係咪都係仆街？","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:48:49.000Z","uid":59222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3983df8c44d1250c39e3ccfda293c063c6cd3c","tid":1562242,"uid":59222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"係黨鐵做黃衫人係咪都係仆街？<br />\n你公司奶共逼你去撐警大會你係咪都係仆街？<br />\n所有公務員又係咪都係仆街？<br />\n<br />\n或者你幫藥廠做packing但間藥廠抬高啲藥嘅價錢好多普通人都冇錢買藥，咁你又係咪仆街？<br />\n地產霸權下你做長實office boy又係咪仆街？<br />\n<br />\n如果全世界啲私營公營機構都某程度上仆街<br />\n咁仲可以做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7677f5c05bc3b18f99e8ae78e7c1fadbf8b275ee","tid":1562242,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbn